item.title: CVE-2023-0388|2023-04-24T18:30:54.683Z -- unknown -- random%20text
item.description: The Random Text WordPress plugin through 0.3.0 does not properly sanitize and escape a parameter before using it in a SQL statement, leading to a SQL injection exploitable by any authenticated users, such as subscribers.
